{"tid":1515095,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[文革2.0]國泰更新員工守則　鼓勵舉報違反守則情況","createTime":"2019-08-29T04:02:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T08:41:12.000Z","uid":68738,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7313fdc580cc2635d35186bcf0225aa25608d062","tid":1515095,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:02:45.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】國泰航空更新員工行為守則，表明對員工參與非法活動會採取零容忍的態度，又鼓勵員工舉報任何懷疑違反守則的情況。<br />\n<br />\n國泰向員工發內部通告，指近日有關解僱員工的報道中有很多錯誤資訊，令員工感到焦慮，公司不會評論個別個案，但向員工保證，解僱決定是經過高層正式及謹慎檢視。國泰對員工參與非法活動會採取零容忍的態度，亦不容許員工使用公司資源表達政治意見。<br />\n<br />\n通告指出，公司需要建立服從的文化，因此鼓勵員工舉報身邊任何懷疑違反守則的情況，公司會跟進調查並保護舉報人的身分。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=360861&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D360861%26refer%3DShare&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRtnRRycoFBIefads3zMUO1U%3D&h=c104ff3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D360861%26refer%3DShare&h=d05aabb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=360861&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"dc539474170b6efec1685b4716a6261e77ca4142","tid":1515095,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:07:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2c4653f9ec08ebbf30202604034efc1d7a209e","tid":1515095,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:08:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1515044\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1515044</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入黎投票<br />\n<br />\n「連登共識」 8 3 1 遊 行 宣言"},{"pid":"6f1299af77e263d844a2ca289504928533a8cba2","tid":1515095,"uid":112581,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:11:33.000Z","msg":"國泰班condom一d